  _npcId: officer_james
  _displayName: Officer James
  _initialDialogueText: 'Thanks for coming.


    A man named Daniel Carter disappeared
    from Room 6 about an hour ago.


    There''s no sign of a struggle. No body.
    Just people who aren''t telling the whole truth.


    I need you to start with
    the receptionist. She was the last person to see him alive.'
